snippet.title: Gojira - "Born For One Thing" | Haider Ali (Guitar Cover) #Shorts
snippet.description:
“Born For One Thing” by @Gojira from the album Fortitude — released in 2021 under @Roadrunner Records, and produced by Joe Duplantier at Silver Cord Studio in Queens, NY, USA — guitar performance by @Haider Ali.

• Subscribe
https://www.youtube.com/haidertonight?sub_confirmation=1

• Thoughts
Hey, folks. Ever since I heard @Gojira's new record, I wanted to cover it in its' entirety, and starting with this killer single, I will be covering more from this record this year. Even though it's a short one, I hope you guys dig it. I really had fun playing this one, folks. Cheers!
